Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:02:00.18,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}那个时候的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:03.94,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}戴着无法飞翔的螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.48,0:02:07.90,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}抬头仰望着半分天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.94,0:02:11.40,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}一路赤脚追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:15.78,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}始终如此的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:18.91,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}也许一直在误解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:22.25,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}持有自信迎面生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:32.46,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:35.59,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}为了能够永久珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:44.48,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这份心情  一定会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.65,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}旋转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.44,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}持有着这魔法之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.57,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}眼泪与Sunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:56.03,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}溶于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:03:00.12,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}寂寞的人的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:02.66,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}会有梦想绽放
